I’ve tried a few other apps like this before and this is honestly the first one that actually. Me the one dollar like they said that they were on top of that every time I go back into this app and check it out it truly just keeps getting better and better. It’s they’re well written. It’s nothing like you’ve ever seen before you know the information that I’ve been getting out of this app. It’s unique completely original and I literally love that so much less I was just out and I literally got this opportunity asked me if I wanted to fill out a review and make $10 so yeah this is 100% legit. title: Scam & Lies
text: Believe what the other reviews are saying even though the developers response is always “we never charge without consent”. That is a lie. Their “directions” on how to cancel a subscription that you will get charged for even though you didn’t sign up for one is purposefully vague and misleading. Reported to Apple. You should also report to Apple or Google store so that there is awareness of this example of fraud. And PS developer who responds to negative reviews. You will waste even more of my time telling me to reach out to an already shaded and misleading support team. Thanks but no thanks. User beware. Developers beware. Karma is swift.
